dimension: 29 x 20 in. (73.66 x 50.8 cm) (sheet, as printed)
text: This artwork is part of the series COVID-19: Labor Camp Report. Artist's statement on this artwork originally published on the @laborcamp Instagram account: 60,000 more people getting sick every day? Let’s all go out and celebrate! Let’s go all out!
title: July 14, 2020: All GO OUT!
